Kuwombera kwa '''mzikiti ya Christchurch''' kunali [[Right-wing terror attacks|kuopsa koopsya]] kwa [[White supremacist|azungu]] ku Al Noor Mosque ndi Linwood Islamic Center ku [[Christchurch]] , [[New Zealand]] , pa [[Jumu'ah|Lachisanu pemphero]] pa 15 March 2019.  Anthu osachepera 49 anaphedwa pa kuwombera ndipo anthu oposa 20 anavulala.  Anthu atatu akudandaula anamangidwa ndi mlandu umodzi.  Nkhondoyi inanenedwa kuti ndi ndondomeko ya [[Terrorist attack|zigawenga]] ndi nduna yaikulu ya New Zealand [[Jacinda Ardern]] ndi maboma osiyanasiyana padziko lonse. Nkhondoyi ndi yomwe inachitika kwambiri ku New Zealand kuyambira mu 1943, [[Featherston prisoner of war camp|mndende wa Featherston wa ndende]] yomwe anthu 49 anaphedwa.  Chinanso chinali [[List of massacres in New Zealand|chowombera]] choyamba [[List of massacres in New Zealand|ku New Zealand]] kuyambira 1997 [[Raurimu massacre|kuphedwa kwa Raurimu]]. 

== Kukumana ==
Kuukira kumeneku kunayambira pa Al Noor Mosque, Riccarton ndi Linwood Islamic Center, pa 13:40 pa 15 March 2019 [[Time in New Zealand#Daylight saving time (DST)|NZDT]] (05:40 [[UTC]] ). Apolisi adapeza mabomba awiri galimoto. Nkhondo [[New Zealand Defence Force|Yachilendo ku New Zealand]] inawadetsa popanda chochitika.  

=== Al Noor Msikiti, Riccarton ===
Munthu wina wothamanga kwambiri athamanga ku Mosque Al Noor ku Deans Ave, [[Riccarton, New Zealand|Riccarton cha]] m'ma 1.40pm. The Al Noor chowombelera [[livestreamed]] mphindi 16 za nkhondo yake pa [[Facebook Live]] , kumene iye kudziwika monga 28 wazaka [[Australian white supremacist|azungu Australia]] Zaka zoyambirira za livestream zinasonyeza woyendetsa galimotoyo akuyendetsa galimoto yake kumsasa ndipo akumvetsera nyimbo ya [[Serbian language|Chiserbia]] yomwe ikukondwerera [[Radovan Karadžić]] , yemwe anapezeka ndi mlandu wa [[Genocide against Bosnian Muslims|kuphedwa kwa Asilamu a ku Bosnia]]. Mfuti zomwe ankagwiritsa ntchito phokosoli zinkalembedwa ndi zolemba zoyera zomwe zimatchulidwa anthu kuchokera ku mbiri yakale mpaka kumbuyo kwa [[Crusades|nkhondo]] zomwe zinkachita nkhondo ndi Asilamu.  Mabukuwa anaphatikizapo [[Internet meme|intaneti]] zambiri, ndipo dzina la Ebba Åkerlund anali pamwamba pa mfuti, yemwe anavutitsidwa ndi [[2017 Stockholm truck attack|zigawenga zachisilamu ku Stockholm]] , anaphedwa ndi kutchetcha galimoto.Anthu mazana atatu kapena asanu akhoza kukhala ali mumsasa, kupita ku [[Friday Prayer|Pemphero la Lachisanu]] , panthawi ya kuwombera.  Mzinda wina wa mzikitiwu unauza olemba nkhani kuti adamuona athawira mumsasawo ndipo akuponya zida zomwe zinkawombera pamsewu pomwe adathawa.  

=== Linwood Islamic Center ===
Wothamanga wachiwiri anaukira Linwood Islamic Center. Msonkhano wina unabwereranso moto.  Apolisi adatsimikizira kuti "ndizowonongeka panthawi imodzi."  

